import React from 'react'

const Nav = ({search,setSearch}) => {
  return (
    <nav className="Nav">
      <form className="searchForm" onSubmit={(e)=>e.preventDefault()}>
        <label htmlFor="search">Search Post</label>
        <input
          id="search"
          type = "text"
          placeholder="Search Post">
            value = {search}
            onch
        ></input>
      </form>
      </nav>
  )
}

export default Nav
